Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community ( hereinafter referred to as the « Treaty ') , and in particular to Article 106 ( 1 ) thereof , and to Articles 16 and 26.4 of the Statute of the European System of Central Banks and of the European Central Bank ( hereinafter referred to as the « Statute ') , Whereas : ( 1 )
