( 2 ) OJ L 134 , 30.4.2004 , p. 114 .
Directive as last amended by Council Directive 2006/97 / EC ( OJ L 363 , 20.12.2006 , p. 107 ) .
( 3 ) OJ L 248 , 16.9.2002 , p. 1 .
